PUT http://localhost:3000/api/user/validation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "code": "111111" }

### Prueba 7.3: Validación - Intento fallido 3
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/user/validation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "code": "222222" }

### Prueba 7.4: Validación - BLOQUEO (Debe dar 429 Too Many Requests)
